1
00:00:38,420 --> 00:00:41,060
=How to Train Your Killer=

2
00:00:41,060 --> 00:00:43,900
=Episode 26=

3
00:00:44,520 --> 00:00:45,470
Who are you?

4
00:00:45,470 --> 00:00:46,310
Such daring!

5
00:00:51,560 --> 00:00:52,400
Move!

6
00:01:06,310 --> 00:01:07,150
Let her go!

7
00:01:08,230 --> 00:01:09,510
If you truly care for her,

8
00:01:10,600 --> 00:01:11,950
you could trade your life for hers.

9
00:01:13,150 --> 00:01:13,990
Your Highness.

10
00:01:14,710 --> 00:01:15,550
Your Highness.

11
00:01:15,680 --> 00:01:16,520
What's wrong?

12
00:01:17,120 --> 00:01:18,150
You can't bear to?

13
00:01:19,430 --> 00:01:20,710
- Well...
- Wait.

14
00:01:21,840 --> 00:01:22,870
Aside from my life,

15
00:01:23,310 --> 00:01:24,920
I will give you anything you desire.

16
00:01:28,760 --> 00:01:30,710
I want you to step down as Crown Prince

17
00:01:31,430 --> 00:01:34,200
and hand the realm over to another.

18
00:01:37,040 --> 00:01:37,950
The realm?

19
00:01:38,350 --> 00:01:39,400
Can you truly take it?

20
00:01:39,590 --> 00:01:40,680
Will you give it or not?

21
00:01:41,560 --> 00:01:43,040
If I were to favor beauty

22
00:01:43,040 --> 00:01:44,310
over the realm itself,

23
00:01:45,070 --> 00:01:46,680
would that not make me a foolish ruler?

24
00:01:47,430 --> 00:01:48,350
Therefore,

25
00:01:49,480 --> 00:01:50,510
for the imperial throne,

26
00:01:50,950 --> 00:01:52,230
you would give up everything?

27
00:01:53,350 --> 00:01:55,000
I do not seek the imperial throne,

28
00:01:56,120 --> 00:01:58,150
but the peace of the people
under the realm.

29
00:01:58,150 --> 00:01:59,710
If it is truly for the people,

30
00:02:00,560 --> 00:02:02,230
then sacrificing one Crown Princess

31
00:02:02,430 --> 00:02:03,430
would not mean much.

32
00:02:04,950 --> 00:02:06,430
I'll give you three breaths.

33
00:02:06,790 --> 00:02:07,640
Three,

34
00:02:10,030 --> 00:02:10,870
two,

35
00:02:17,430 --> 00:02:18,270
one.

36
00:02:19,000 --> 00:02:19,840
No!

37
00:02:21,750 --> 00:02:22,590
Qingyao!

38
00:02:23,400 --> 00:02:24,240
Qingyao!

39
00:02:24,800 --> 00:02:27,000
Qingyao, Qingyao!

40
00:02:40,800 --> 00:02:42,400
You heartless man!

41
00:02:53,430 --> 00:02:54,360
Your Highness.

42
00:02:57,000 --> 00:02:57,840
Qingyao.

43
00:02:58,400 --> 00:02:59,240
Qingyao.

44
00:03:00,430 --> 00:03:01,270
I'm fine.

45
00:03:05,000 --> 00:03:06,000
I told you earlier.

46
00:03:06,130 --> 00:03:07,030
He knows martial arts.

47
00:03:14,310 --> 00:03:15,400
Hero Shi?

48
00:03:15,800 --> 00:03:16,710
It's you.

49
00:03:17,360 --> 00:03:19,000
You've figured it out now, haven't you?

50
00:03:20,910 --> 00:03:22,000
If he chooses me,

51
00:03:22,430 --> 00:03:23,360
I'd still feel uneasy

52
00:03:23,360 --> 00:03:24,800
to lay the whole plan before him.

53
00:03:26,240 --> 00:03:27,080
Come on.

54
00:03:27,560 --> 00:03:28,630
What are you talking about?

55
00:03:29,400 --> 00:03:30,240
Hero Shi,

56
00:03:30,400 --> 00:03:31,680
why are you treating me this way?

57
00:03:31,910 --> 00:03:33,520
He's not Hero Shi.

58
00:03:34,560 --> 00:03:36,470
He is the assassin from that night.

59
00:03:38,360 --> 00:03:39,200
What?

60
00:03:40,200 --> 00:03:41,670
Isn't he the guard send by Minister Gu

61
00:03:41,670 --> 00:03:42,680
to protect you?

62
00:03:44,910 --> 00:03:45,750
Your Highness,

63
00:03:47,190 --> 00:03:48,560
what I'm about to say next

64
00:03:49,020 --> 00:03:50,290
may sound utterly inconceivable.

65
00:03:52,000 --> 00:03:53,680
But you have no choice
but to believe it.

66
00:03:54,430 --> 00:03:56,310
She is me.

67
00:03:56,960 --> 00:03:58,430
I am him.

68
00:03:58,550 --> 00:04:00,150
On the night he tried to take your life,

69
00:04:00,840 --> 00:04:02,120
we swapped bodies.

70
00:04:06,430 --> 00:04:07,310
That's how

71
00:04:08,910 --> 00:04:09,750
it happened.

72
00:04:14,000 --> 00:04:15,360
Such an absurd tale!

73
00:04:15,500 --> 00:04:16,770
How am I supposed to believe you?

74
00:04:19,000 --> 00:04:19,840
Your Highness,

75
00:04:20,390 --> 00:04:21,430
I truly am Qingyao.

76
00:04:21,430 --> 00:04:22,270
I don't believe it.

77
00:04:27,160 --> 00:04:28,310
If you truly doubt me,

78
00:04:29,630 --> 00:04:30,870
then kill me with your sword.

79
00:04:31,800 --> 00:04:32,640
Your Highness!

80
00:04:33,600 --> 00:04:35,120
Anyway, there's no turning back for us.

81
00:04:35,120 --> 00:04:35,960
Isn't that so?

82
00:04:37,120 --> 00:04:37,960
Go ahead.

83
00:04:42,630 --> 00:04:44,720
I still need some proof.

84
00:04:46,430 --> 00:04:47,270
What kind of proof?

85
00:04:47,950 --> 00:04:48,870
There's one thing

86
00:04:49,390 --> 00:04:50,950
that only Qingyao and I know about it.

87
00:04:53,950 --> 00:04:55,190
Do you know why Qingyao

88
00:04:55,460 --> 00:04:56,720
has always been afraid of water?

89
00:05:01,480 --> 00:05:03,830
When I entered the palace
for a banquet at eight,

90
00:05:03,830 --> 00:05:04,970
I wandered off while playing.

91
00:05:05,430 --> 00:05:07,360
By accident, I saw you
fall into the deep pond.

92
00:05:07,800 --> 00:05:08,830
I jumped in to rescue you,

93
00:05:08,830 --> 00:05:10,490
and swallowed several mouthfuls
of water.

94
00:05:10,490 --> 00:05:11,500
I nearly drowned that day.

95
00:05:13,390 --> 00:05:14,430
How would I know

96
00:05:14,430 --> 00:05:16,240
if Qingyao has told you this?

97
00:05:16,240 --> 00:05:17,240
Because you once said,

98
00:05:17,900 --> 00:05:19,840
there was something strange
about that incident.

99
00:05:20,630 --> 00:05:21,560
To keep the secret safe,

100
00:05:21,830 --> 00:05:22,950
and avoid arousing suspicion,

101
00:05:22,950 --> 00:05:23,790
all these years,

102
00:05:24,270 --> 00:05:25,510
I've never told a soul.

103
00:05:30,120 --> 00:05:31,000
In this vast world,

104
00:05:32,310 --> 00:05:33,630
there truly are such things.

105
00:05:41,040 --> 00:05:42,950
Why are you telling me all this?

106
00:05:46,800 --> 00:05:48,040
Because yesterday,

107
00:05:50,070 --> 00:05:51,510
we finally reached a dead end.

108
00:05:52,160 --> 00:05:53,000
A dead end?

109
00:05:53,680 --> 00:05:54,830
My true identity

110
00:05:55,400 --> 00:05:57,150
is a killer
from the Wind and Rain Pavilion.

111
00:05:57,310 --> 00:05:58,920
The one who ordered me
to take your life

112
00:06:00,040 --> 00:06:01,750
was Prime Minister Gu Pingzhang.

113
00:06:05,600 --> 00:06:07,160
For the sake of seizing the throne,

114
00:06:07,900 --> 00:06:08,790
he even went so far as

115
00:06:10,750 --> 00:06:12,480
to sacrifice his own daughter.

116
00:06:13,600 --> 00:06:15,000
The day I came to kill you

117
00:06:15,310 --> 00:06:16,870
was the night of your wedding.

118
00:06:31,600 --> 00:06:34,830
Qingyao and I accidentally
fell into the water.

119
00:06:36,600 --> 00:06:37,440
That day,

120
00:06:37,990 --> 00:06:38,830
the thunder was loud,

121
00:06:38,830 --> 00:06:39,990
and the rain was pouring down.

122
00:06:40,430 --> 00:06:42,830
We swapped bodies in the water.

123
00:06:51,920 --> 00:06:52,800
This night

124
00:06:54,160 --> 00:06:55,800
is truly long.

125
00:06:58,750 --> 00:07:00,270
Why are you telling me this?

126
00:07:01,600 --> 00:07:03,000
Because we only wish to stay alive.

127
00:07:03,830 --> 00:07:04,670
No.

128
00:07:05,070 --> 00:07:06,430
Even if we meet our end,

129
00:07:06,950 --> 00:07:08,560
we'll still strike at each other.

130
00:07:10,830 --> 00:07:11,720
Only you,

131
00:07:13,310 --> 00:07:16,000
the Crown Prince of today, can help us.

132
00:07:20,830 --> 00:07:22,040
One last question.

133
00:07:23,120 --> 00:07:24,600
Why choose to trust me?

134
00:07:24,800 --> 00:07:26,600
Because you are willing
to let go of Qingyao.

135
00:07:28,070 --> 00:07:29,920
You cannot abandon the realm
and its people.

136
00:07:30,190 --> 00:07:31,480
Compared to Gu Pingzhang,

137
00:07:32,000 --> 00:07:33,550
you are more likely to be a wise ruler.

138
00:08:02,000 --> 00:08:02,840
Your Highness.

139
00:08:11,600 --> 00:08:12,440
Your Highness,

140
00:08:12,800 --> 00:08:14,050
you've stayed awake all night.

141
00:08:14,430 --> 00:08:15,950
The realm is about to change hands.

142
00:08:15,950 --> 00:08:17,240
How could I possibly sleep now?

143
00:08:18,460 --> 00:08:19,460
You've found a plan then?

144
00:08:21,070 --> 00:08:22,270
Not exactly a plan.

145
00:08:22,630 --> 00:08:23,950
But it might be worth a try.

146
00:08:33,960 --> 00:08:34,800
Let's go.

147
00:08:34,960 --> 00:08:36,360
They've been waiting quite a while.

148
00:08:47,960 --> 00:08:48,800
Your Highness.

149
00:08:53,940 --> 00:08:55,100
(To the Crown Prince)

150
00:08:55,100 --> 00:08:56,570
Father asked me
to deliver it to you.

151
00:09:10,390 --> 00:09:12,510
(The matters in Jiangnan
have been resolved.)

152
00:09:17,200 --> 00:09:18,040
I appreciate it.

153
00:09:18,550 --> 00:09:20,000
Give my regards to General Shen.

154
00:09:31,480 --> 00:09:32,320
Qingyao,

155
00:09:33,020 --> 00:09:34,170
please take care of yourself.

156
00:09:34,840 --> 00:09:35,680
Mm.

157
00:09:46,510 --> 00:09:47,350
Your Highness,

158
00:09:48,200 --> 00:09:49,140
what is this?

159
00:09:50,300 --> 00:09:51,600
I had already asked General Shen

160
00:09:51,600 --> 00:09:52,960
to place spies across Jiangnan.

161
00:09:53,400 --> 00:09:55,740
Minister Gu used disaster relief
in the south as a pretext,

162
00:09:55,900 --> 00:09:57,890
but in fact it was to stockpile
military supplies.

163
00:09:58,910 --> 00:10:00,790
General Shen's forces
have already moved ahead.

164
00:10:01,320 --> 00:10:02,440
But what concerns me is

165
00:10:03,000 --> 00:10:04,660
your father's informants
within the court.

166
00:10:05,720 --> 00:10:07,000
Those who share his schemes

167
00:10:07,670 --> 00:10:09,870
remain as a lingering threat
in the capital.

168
00:10:13,870 --> 00:10:14,710
Qingyao,

169
00:10:14,730 --> 00:10:16,550
you grew up
in the Prime Minister's Residence,

170
00:10:16,550 --> 00:10:17,670
so you should know with whom

171
00:10:17,670 --> 00:10:19,340
your father usually keeps
close relations.

172
00:10:36,000 --> 00:10:36,840
Get out.

173
00:10:38,240 --> 00:10:39,200
Your Highness.

174
00:10:40,030 --> 00:10:41,720
Your Highness.

175
00:10:44,870 --> 00:10:46,270
Oh, it's the young hero.

176
00:10:46,270 --> 00:10:47,110
What a coincidence.

177
00:10:47,320 --> 00:10:48,870
We meet again.

178
00:10:50,630 --> 00:10:51,790
I should have guessed long ago

179
00:10:52,100 --> 00:10:54,070
that you wouldn't wander
through the martial world

180
00:10:54,150 --> 00:10:55,510
for no reason.

181
00:10:56,440 --> 00:10:58,030
If not for that assassination attempt,

182
00:10:58,300 --> 00:11:00,440
I wouldn't dare involve people
from the martial world.

183
00:11:01,510 --> 00:11:02,350
However,

184
00:11:02,720 --> 00:11:04,080
now happens to be an opportunity.

185
00:11:06,510 --> 00:11:07,440
So,

186
00:11:07,900 --> 00:11:09,700
when you said you would
take me out to relax,

187
00:11:09,700 --> 00:11:11,000
you were lying to me.

188
00:11:12,360 --> 00:11:13,320
Not entirely.

189
00:11:13,750 --> 00:11:14,720
Taking Hero Shi...

190
00:11:14,960 --> 00:11:15,800
Shi...

191
00:11:16,080 --> 00:11:17,480
Qingyao out to relax

192
00:11:18,390 --> 00:11:19,270
is important too.

193
00:11:24,000 --> 00:11:25,510
Then I must look rather foolish.

194
00:11:27,630 --> 00:11:28,910
Before Minister Gu,

195
00:11:29,480 --> 00:11:30,440
we all look foolish.

196
00:11:34,510 --> 00:11:35,840
Hero Shi knows all the strongholds

197
00:11:35,840 --> 00:11:37,440
of the Wind and Rain Pavilion.

198
00:11:37,840 --> 00:11:38,680
Your mission

199
00:11:39,030 --> 00:11:41,240
is to help him

200
00:11:41,240 --> 00:11:42,270
wipe them out completely.

201
00:11:43,300 --> 00:11:44,540
Eunuch Leng will act in secret,

202
00:11:44,540 --> 00:11:45,750
to shield you along the way.

203
00:11:46,550 --> 00:11:47,750
Once the task is done,

204
00:11:48,400 --> 00:11:49,880
you will be granted rank and rewards.

205
00:11:50,150 --> 00:11:51,240
- Yes.
- Yes.

206
00:12:27,030 --> 00:12:27,870
Father.

207
00:12:33,670 --> 00:12:35,080
My son,

208
00:12:35,840 --> 00:12:37,720
may you be a wise ruler.

209
00:12:46,000 --> 00:12:47,000
Father.

210
00:12:53,030 --> 00:12:55,200
By the will of Heaven,

211
00:12:55,510 --> 00:12:56,550
the Emperor hereby decrees,

212
00:12:56,790 --> 00:12:59,600
bandits have been causing trouble
in the northern borderlands,

213
00:12:59,750 --> 00:13:01,440
plotting rebellion.

214
00:13:02,270 --> 00:13:04,240
The Prime Minister Gu Pingzhang
is appointed

215
00:13:04,240 --> 00:13:06,080
to go and negotiate peace.

216
00:13:06,840 --> 00:13:08,240
By imperial decree.

217
00:13:09,910 --> 00:13:11,360
I accept the decree.

218
00:13:12,150 --> 00:13:13,630
(Ling Yu disrupted my father's mind)

219
00:13:13,630 --> 00:13:14,910
(with an imperial decree,)

220
00:13:15,150 --> 00:13:16,870
(transferring him out of the capital,)

221
00:13:21,770 --> 00:13:23,080
(and then, using the same tactic,)

222
00:13:23,080 --> 00:13:25,290
(dismissed court officials
on good terms with my father)

223
00:13:25,290 --> 00:13:27,870
(on charges of corruption
and dereliction of duty.)

224
00:13:32,360 --> 00:13:33,910
(Father's wings were clipped.)

225
00:13:34,200 --> 00:13:35,660
(Only then did he wake to the truth,)

226
00:13:35,660 --> 00:13:36,720
(he hurried back.)

227
00:13:37,320 --> 00:13:39,510
(But it was already too late.)

228
00:14:01,300 --> 00:14:02,650
(It was not until this very moment)

229
00:14:02,750 --> 00:14:03,870
(that I finally understood)

230
00:14:04,600 --> 00:14:07,790
(that the once reserved
Crown Prince Ling Yu)

231
00:14:07,790 --> 00:14:09,270
(had such a hidden side.)

232
00:14:14,720 --> 00:14:15,560
Your Highness.

233
00:14:17,670 --> 00:14:18,510
You've come.

234
00:14:20,550 --> 00:14:21,720
From the look of this,

235
00:14:22,000 --> 00:14:23,250
it seems you have already won.

236
00:14:24,480 --> 00:14:25,550
I have an awkward request

237
00:14:25,550 --> 00:14:26,630
for coming here this time.

238
00:14:28,150 --> 00:14:29,000
Speak freely.

239
00:14:34,030 --> 00:14:34,870
Your Highness,

240
00:14:36,840 --> 00:14:38,240
could you spare my father's life?

241
00:14:40,240 --> 00:14:41,840
Treason is a grave crime.

242
00:14:42,790 --> 00:14:44,390
This is but my humble plea.

243
00:14:44,390 --> 00:14:46,200
It doesn't matter if you refuse.

244
00:14:49,240 --> 00:14:51,030
By rights, you've accomplished
a great deed,

245
00:14:51,320 --> 00:14:52,790
and I ought to reward you accordingly.

246
00:14:54,630 --> 00:14:55,550
However,

247
00:14:56,000 --> 00:14:57,480
Minister Gu still holds power

248
00:14:57,480 --> 00:14:58,720
within the martial world.

249
00:14:59,390 --> 00:15:00,910
When the dust finally settles,

250
00:15:01,390 --> 00:15:02,630
I will make the final decision.

251
00:15:03,550 --> 00:15:04,390
What do you think?

252
00:15:04,750 --> 00:15:06,200
Then, may I go with them

253
00:15:06,200 --> 00:15:07,400
to the Wind and Rain Pavilion?

254
00:15:07,810 --> 00:15:08,840
That's far too dangerous.

255
00:15:10,960 --> 00:15:11,800
Rest assured,

256
00:15:11,850 --> 00:15:13,280
Eunuch Leng will be there to assist.

257
00:15:13,320 --> 00:15:14,390
The lackeys at the Pavilion

258
00:15:14,390 --> 00:15:15,450
can't stir up much trouble.

259
00:15:15,550 --> 00:15:17,720
The martial world
is deeply entangled now.

260
00:15:17,800 --> 00:15:19,750
The Pavilion is full of skilled fighters.

261
00:15:19,750 --> 00:15:20,950
Their methods are underhanded.

262
00:15:21,200 --> 00:15:22,270
And Hero Shi

263
00:15:22,550 --> 00:15:24,120
has already lost all his inner strength,

264
00:15:25,000 --> 00:15:26,550
so this won't be an easy task.

265
00:15:28,840 --> 00:15:29,910
Turns out

266
00:15:30,790 --> 00:15:32,150
you're worried about him.

267
00:15:44,710 --> 00:15:47,310
♪When a breeze passes by♪

268
00:15:47,830 --> 00:15:51,150
♪The sand and wind burn with longing♪

269
00:15:51,150 --> 00:15:53,790
♪Fearless even when thirst
goes unquenched♪

270
00:15:54,110 --> 00:15:57,270
♪Like a camel wandering
with eyes closed♪

271
00:15:57,630 --> 00:16:00,590
♪When the rain quietly settles♪

272
00:16:00,590 --> 00:16:03,910
♪I think of our sorrow yet unknown♪

273
00:16:04,110 --> 00:16:06,830
♪No need to hum the song of the wind♪

274
00:16:06,990 --> 00:16:10,630
♪Ignoring the sky darkening before us♪

275
00:16:10,790 --> 00:16:12,390
♪I finally understood that truth♪

276
00:16:12,390 --> 00:16:13,870
♪Yet you have already faded away♪

277
00:16:14,070 --> 00:16:15,710
♪I lose my way in the night♪

278
00:16:15,710 --> 00:16:17,190
♪Not knowing how to still my heart♪

279
00:16:17,190 --> 00:16:18,870
♪Loving you feels like lifetimes apart♪

280
00:16:18,870 --> 00:16:21,830
♪Yet longing flows back into verse♪

281
00:16:22,270 --> 00:16:24,710
♪For you and me to meet again♪

282
00:16:25,150 --> 00:16:27,990
♪We must cross a thousand years
of promises♪

283
00:16:28,270 --> 00:16:30,350
♪In the pouring rain♪

284
00:16:30,350 --> 00:16:34,710
♪As if you are still by my side♪
